00:49:35.640 --> 00:49:39.190
However, a spherical aberration
will come in, for example,

00:49:39.190 --> 00:49:41.055
if you--

00:49:41.055 --> 00:49:41.930
let's take this case.

00:49:46.690 --> 00:49:50.340
Yeah, if you move
