00:49:50.340 --> 00:49:53.530
then the plane wave of
coming out will be aberrated.

00:49:53.530 --> 00:49:54.390
The same here.

00:49:54.390 --> 00:49:56.670
If you tilt this plane wave.

00:49:56.670 --> 00:50:00.840
Again, the point image
will be aberrated.

00:50:00.840 --> 00:50:03.710
Actually, it would be
